1956;;Everything but the Truth;;American;;Jerry Hopper;;Maureen O'Hara, John Forsythe;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Everything_but_the_Truth;;A schoolboy who has been urged to always tell the truth blurts out that an uncle of his has received a payoff from a politician. Chaos ensues, as teacher Joan Madison fights the school principal's decision to expel the boy from classes and enlists a newspaper columnist, Ernie Miller, to help support her cause.